# LDM College ERP — Recovery Walkthrough

## Completed Fixes

### 1. RBAC Enforcement ✅

**Problem:** Any authenticated user could access `/admin/*` endpoints.  
**Solution:** Created [RoleMiddleware.php](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20new%20updae%202.0/api/RoleMiddleware.php) and applied [adminOnly()](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20new%20updae%202.0/api/RoleMiddleware.php#59-66) to 16 admin routes.

#### Changes Made
- [RoleMiddleware.php](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20new%20updae%202.0/api/RoleMiddleware.php) — New middleware with [requireRole()](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20new%20updae%202.0/api/RoleMiddleware.php#16-58), [adminOnly()](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20new%20updae%202.0/api/RoleMiddleware.php#59-66), [teacherOrAdmin()](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20new%20updae%202.0/api/RoleMiddleware.php#75-82)
- [index.php](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20new%20updae%202.0/api/index.php) — Added `->add(RoleMiddleware::adminOnly())` to all admin routes

#### Verification
```bash
# Student trying to access admin endpoint → 403 Forbidden
curl -H "Authorization: Bearer $STUDENT_TOKEN" http://localhost:8000/admin/users
# {"success":false,"error":"Forbidden","your_role":"student"}

# Admin accessing same endpoint → 200 OK
curl -H "Authorization: Bearer $ADMIN_TOKEN" http://localhost:8000/admin/users
# {"success":true,"users":[...]}
```

---

### 2. Attendance API ✅

**Problem:** `POST /attendance/mark` was a stub returning fake success.  
**Solution:** Implemented real DB operations with `gibbonAttendanceLogPerson`.

#### Changes Made
- Replaced stub with full implementation (~200 lines)
- Added `GET /attendance` for fetching class/form group attendance
- Applied [teacherOrAdmin()](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20new%20updae%202.0/api/RoleMiddleware.php#75-82) RBAC to both endpoints

#### API Contract

```bash
# POST /attendance/mark
curl -X POST http://localhost:8000/attendance/mark \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer $TOKEN" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "date": "2026-02-08",
    "records": [
      {"student_id": "0000000002", "code": "001"},
      {"student_id": "0000000003", "code": "004", "comment": "Sick"}
    ]
  }'
# Response: {"success":true,"records_saved":2,"errors":[]}
```

#### DB Evidence

| gibbonPersonID | date | type | context | timestampTaken |
|----------------|------|------|---------|----------------|
| 0000000002 | 2026-02-08 | Present | Person | 2026-02-08 03:27:42 |
| 0000000003 | 2026-02-08 | Absent | Person | 2026-02-08 03:27:42 |

